How to create a package:

ulyaoth-solr8: (includes docs & examples rpm)
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ulyaoth/repository/master/ulyaoth-solr/build-solr8.sh ; chmod +x build-solr8.sh ; ./build-solr8.sh

ulyaoth-solr7: (includes docs & examples rpm)
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ulyaoth/repository/master/ulyaoth-solr/build-solr7.sh ; chmod +x build-solr7.sh ; ./build-solr7.sh

ulyaoth-solr6: (includes docs & examples rpm)
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ulyaoth/repository/master/ulyaoth-solr/build-solr6.sh ; chmod +x build-solr6.sh ; ./build-solr6.sh

ulyaoth-solr5: (includes docs & examples rpm)
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ulyaoth/repository/master/ulyaoth-solr/build-solr5.sh ; chmod +x build-solr5.sh ; ./build-solr5.sh

ulyaoth-solr4: (single rpm)
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ulyaoth/repository/master/ulyaoth-solr/build-solr4.sh ; chmod +x build-solr4.sh ; ./build-solr4.sh